name: Rewards
description:
These artworks are from a web work called 'To The Ghost Nets', hosted on my website www.lewkwilmshurst.co.uk.
They also feature in a show commissioned by the Museum of Contemporary Art Busan - 05-09 2021.
These are some pieces of things. Fragments of the stuff that makes up everything. Maybe they do things together? Maybe they are keys for a lock not yet made?...
